  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/939",
  "title": "implement searching in facet values",
  "body": "For long list of facet values, it would be cool to have an option like \"valuesSearchBox: true\" that would display a searchbox and do the necessary heavy lifting on the helper to display corresponding \"current filters + user facet value query\" facet values.\n\nThis would require the user to have a custom facet values index.\n\nIt may not be that efficient to pass long list of filters to the API but we have to try.\n\ncc @pixelastic @gregquat\n",
